room_title: Escape room "Dinner for Two" by Murfreesboro Escape Room in Murfreesboro
room_description:
FINALLY.
A night out on the town for just the two of us.

We managed to land reservations for a great new place. After our dinner, we stop in the coat closet to grab our things, and then...

CLICK.

The door shuts and locks behind us. We have to get out, the restaurant's about to close, but as we hurriedly try to make our escape, a hidden sight catches our attention.

Maybe there's more to this closet than meets the eye...
